What is form?
-->To collect user input

Tags:

<form>: to create html form for user input

<input>: many forms to get input form

<label>: text field gives label to ur id like name,email,password

input tag 'id= " "'attribute is same for label tag 'for= " "'attribute

type="text" or "radio" or "checkbox" or "date" or "submit,etc

for attribute is used in label for identifing them
id aattribute is used in input for unique identification

placeholder attribute for highligher on input field

